metadata.name: Golden whales
metadata.description:
This artwork is about the waves of life and the inhabitants of the planet who are immersed in them - a cycle of ups and downs illuminated by the rays of hope.
The painting is made on the canvas by a combination of different artistic techniques.
Plaster used for volume, acrylic paint for color and decorative stones for shine.
Size 90x120 cm
Canvas, plaster, acrylic, stones

3400 x 4500 px
